</taxonomicName>
is composed of 
<emphasis id="52C3EA96723CD4568B1C2DC46436FAAC" box="[1052,1122,1260,1285]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="318">bystra</emphasis>
, f. Greek, meaning ‘plug or bung’ referring to dorsal plate, plus 
<emphasis id="52C3EA96723CD4568D2A2C396222FA81" box="[554,630,1297,1320]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="318">coccus</emphasis>
, Gr. for grain or berry, after which the superfamily is named.
</paragraph>
